" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Gestational sac without yolk sac or embryo",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 354px; height: 298px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Transverse view of the uterus shows an abnormally shaped intrauterine gestational sac with mean sac diameter of 31 mm. At this sac size, a yolk sac and embryo should be seen but were not. Findings represent early pregnancy failure. Arrows indicate the empty amnion.",
